comment: Dedmon (ORL) sets the screen on Lawson (HOU) and gives him the opportunity to avoid the contact.
L-Slash Howard (HOU) sets the screen on Payton (ORL) and gives him the opportunity to avoid the contact.
Fournier (ORL) makes contact with the ball prior to making incidental contact with Harden's (HOU) wrist on the shot attempt.
Dedmon (ORL) sets the screen on Brewer (HOU) and gives him the opportunity to avoid the contact.
Oladipo (ORL) makes contact with Harden's (HOU) arm, affecting his drive to the basket and layup attempt.
Dedmon (ORL) makes contact with Brewer's (HOU) head that affects his layup attempt.
[Observable in enhanced video] Harris (ORL) moves his pivot foot heel to toe.
Lawson (HOU) commits a take foul on Napier (ORL).
Harden (HOU) makes contact with Fournier's (ORL) arm that affects his drive to the basket and layup attempt.
Dedmon (ORL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Howard (HOU) who cannot control the alley-oop pass.
Payton (ORL) sets the hand-off screen on Brewer (HOU) without giving him room to avoid the screen and he delivers contact.
Harden (HOU) grabs Harris (ORL) and affects his ability to catch the pass.
Ariza (HOU) and Oladipo (ORL) make incidental contact with one another.
Payton (ORL) cleanly blocks Lawson's (HOU) shot attempt.
Dedmon (ORL) does not have his arms vertical and makes contact with Howard (HOU) as he attempts the layup.
Harden (HOU) drives directly to the basket and the contact made with Oladipo (ORL) is incidental.
Howard (HOU) and Oladipo (ORL) briefly engage then separate away from the ball.
Fournier (ORL) extends his arm into Harden's (HOU) area and contact is initiated by Harden's upward motion.
Fournier (ORL) allows Harden (HOU) to land after the jump shot.
Oladipo (ORL) makes incidental contact after Ariza (HOU) has already released the ball.
As Gordon (ORL) attempts the rebound, Brewer (HOU) pulls his arm down.
[Observable in enhanced video] PXP shows Oladipo (ORL) splits his feet on the perimeter.
Ariza (HOU) makes body to body contact with Fournier (ORL) that affects his RSBQ on the drive to the basket.
Fournier (ORL) allows Harden (HOU) the space to land after the jump shot.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the ball was last touched by Napier (ORL) was upheld.
Howard (HOU) sets the screen on Napier (ORL) and gives him the opportunity to avoid the contact.
Dedmon (ORL) makes contact with Howard (HOU) that affects his ability to secure the pass.
Harden (HOU) runs into and clamps Fournier's (ORL) arm as he drives to the basket.
Oladipo (ORL) commits a take foul on Harden (HOU).
